name: Do they love me?
description:
M.M.I, pt 1: Anxiety

Self-judgment, one of anxiety's defining characteristics. A harsh, violent, and cold voice spewing endless torrent of negativity. 

Museum of Mental Incapabilities is a collection of artworks depicting mental health problems and disorders. Explore and understand what it feels like to live with various mental incapacities. 

Know that you are not alone, there 7.9 billion people in the world, there will always be a person who loves and cares for you.
